Class AbstractUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • AbstractUser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InterfaceUser
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractUserTest.AbstractUserTestExtend, Guest, Receptionist

    public abstract class AbstractUser
extends java.lang.Object
implements InterfaceUser
    Abstract User class. Both Receptionists and Guests will inherit this class. Has all the necessary methods for both of these classes.
    Author:
    Yasir
